owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._generation: Seascape Nft generation that is given as a reward
params._startTime: session start time in unix timestamp

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

setNftFactory(address).notice: Sets a NFT factory that will mint a token for stakers

spend(uint256,uint256).notice: Spend _amount of LP token of type _token into Staking contract.

startSession(uint256,uint256,uint256,uin.notice: Starts a staking session for a finit _period of time, starting from _startTime. The _totalReward of CWS tokens will be distributed in every second. It allows to claim a a _generation Seascape NFT.
